WEBVTT

00:00:00.552 --> 00:00:01.710
-TY SIX

00:00:02.475 --> 00:00:06.817
az in fertsik hot men aroys- aykh aroysgetribn

00:00:06.817 --> 00:00:08.054
fun Gritse

00:00:08.314 --> 00:00:10.080
az zogt mir nokh a mol

00:00:10.305 --> 00:00:14.517
ah di mame iz farshikt un der tate keyn Varshever geto

00:00:15.385 --> 00:00:16.779
un ir oykh?

00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:18.484
NO. ikh bin shoyn nisht geven demolt.

00:00:18.523 --> 00:00:20.221
un vos mit di shvester?

00:00:19.857 --> 00:00:22.416
di shvester zenen geven mitn tatn mit di mame.

00:00:22.185 --> 00:00:25.874
az di dray, di, di ale finef, zenen geven in Var-

00:00:24.497 --> 00:00:28.338
ale dray, ale dray UNK. ye, ye.

00:00:25.915 --> 00:00:28.013
di dray shvester mit di ⟨ts- eltern⟩

00:00:28.013 --> 00:00:29.604
zenen geven in Varshe

00:00:29.610 --> 00:00:31.190
un vu zayt ir geven?

00:00:31.382 --> 00:00:33.941
in Rusland, in Vaysrusland.

00:00:33.643 --> 00:00:35.240
ven zent ir avek

00:00:35.449 --> 00:00:36.759
fun Gritse?

00:00:37.052 --> 00:00:38.278
UNK

00:00:40.630 --> 00:00:41.839
in yanuar

00:00:42.233 --> 00:00:43.914
in yanuar fun fertsik?

00:00:43.802 --> 00:00:45.601
fertsikstn yor

00:00:44.477 --> 00:00:48.015
az ir zayt a- avek mit, mit dem, mit ayer man.

00:00:47.127 --> 00:00:48.251
mit ⟨mayn man⟩.

00:00:48.122 --> 00:00:49.837
mit der tsukunftiker man.

00:00:48.780 --> 00:00:49.786
ye

00:00:51.008 --> 00:00:56.486
un far vos hot ir a- gelo- avekgelozt di shvester? far vos zenen zey nisht mitgekumen mit aykh?

00:00:56.053 --> 00:01:02.188
zey hobn gevolt ⟨BUT⟩ nisht gekent. UNK avek mit aza moyre, m'hot UNK ganen bagrenetsn, m'hot UNK

00:01:02.188 --> 00:01:06.098
UNK oykh bazunder, vi ken men iberlozn di mame ⟨mitn⟩ tatn aleyn?

00:01:06.972 --> 00:01:10.031
az oyf der veg keyn Shidlovtse vu m'hot

00:01:10.031 --> 00:01:16.061
hot men zikh farshribn nakher tsu geyn arbetn barn daytsh. m'hot gezogt me geyt shikn oyf arbet. ver es vil zol ⟨zikh⟩ farshraybn

00:01:16.337 --> 00:01:22.001
iz di eltste gelofn. zi hot zikh farshribn, gezogt az "ikh gey arbetn undz aheym brengen a shtikl broyt ⟨in shtub⟩ UNK"

00:01:23.374 --> 00:01:31.316
hot di yingere nokhgelofn. zi hot oykh gevolt zikh farshraybn. hobn zikh beyde geshlogn, di UNK aheym tsu di mame. di mame iz aleyn

00:01:31.845 --> 00:01:33.543
ober zi iz geganen.

00:01:33.617 --> 00:01:35.720
fun vanet veyst ir az

00:01:34.832 --> 00:01:37.627
di shvester lebt ⟨az zi⟩ hot mir dertseylt.

00:01:38.325 --> 00:01:42.369
az ir hot nisht demolst gevust az zey zenen farshikt keyn Varshe.

00:01:40.772 --> 00:01:43.275
mir hobn in gantsn gornisht gevust

00:01:43.275 --> 00:01:46.802
ABSOLUTELY gornisht. eyn briv UNK fun mayn foter

00:01:46.802 --> 00:01:47.910
AND THAT'S ALL.

00:01:47.910 --> 00:01:49.860
ven der daytsh iz ongefaln oyf Rusland

00:01:49.860 --> 00:01:51.950
hot men aropgenumen di ale

00:01:51.950 --> 00:01:54.240
in lager bin ikh geven di, di, di

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:56.590
UNK gornisht gevust.

00:01:57.090 --> 00:02:00.661
bin geven in a lager nakher. fun tfise hot men undz gefirt in a lager arayn.

00:01:59.740 --> 00:02:03.919
az ir hot gezogt epes az der tate hot geheysn antloyfn, yo?

00:02:03.638 --> 00:02:07.007
der tate hot undz gefirt. ikh bin aheymgeganen nokh ontuekhts

00:02:07.350 --> 00:02:10.567
in fertsikstn yor bin ikh tsurik aheymgan oyf di grenets

00:02:10.776 --> 00:02:16.997
bin arayn UNK ⟨lomir⟩ epes a kleydl, a vos. bin geven naket un borves. kh'hob nisht gehat vos ⟨ontsutun⟩, bin ikh avek azoy antlofn.

00:02:17.442 --> 00:02:19.748
ikh bin tsurikgeganen nokh di grenets.

00:02:20.530 --> 00:02:22.703
hot der tate undz gefirt in di DWORZEC

00:02:22.703 --> 00:02:27.999
GLOWNY in Varshe. hot undz, m'hot gezogt "antloyfts, kinder, vi vayt ets kent nor"

00:02:30.165 --> 00:02:32.626
ven me zetst nisht mayn tatn ⟨an⟩ PAWIAK

00:02:32.626 --> 00:02:36.133
volt er oykhet antlofn. er hot shoyn nisht gekent geyn oyf di fis.

00:02:35.734 --> 00:02:38.158
az ven iz dos geven vos ir zent tsurik?

00:02:38.417 --> 00:02:41.246
in fertsikstn yor bin ikh tsurikgeganen.

00:02:39.919 --> 00:02:41.296
in velkhn monat?

00:02:42.788 --> 00:02:43.929
gedenk nisht.

00:02:44.492 --> 00:02:47.220
in dos iz geven dos letste mol vos ir hot gezen

00:02:46.078 --> 00:02:48.417
dos letste mol vos ikh hob gezen mayn foter.

00:02:48.458 --> 00:02:49.751
un di mame oykh.

00:02:49.403 --> 00:02:51.624
UNK

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:51.641
un di shvester

00:02:51.765 --> 00:02:55.303
ikh bin tsu zey geven in BAKERY bay mayn HUSBAND

00:02:56.507 --> 00:03:04.466
⟨nu, zi hot⟩ fun mir gelakht. "ets fort avek, ets fort avek. ze nor, me handlt un fardint. m'hot broyt tsu esn." zey hobn nisht gevust vos geyt ⟨in⟩ UNK

00:03:05.299 --> 00:03:08.668
ober ikh hob nisht gevolt zen ⟨dem⟩ daytsh. m'iz avek.

00:03:09.957 --> 00:03:11.621
az vu zayt ir gegangen?

00:03:12.657 --> 00:03:14.490
nokh ZAREBY KOSCIELNE.

00:03:14.867 --> 00:03:15.975
vu?

00:03:14.985 --> 00:03:17.915
keyn Malkin. zenen mir dos ershte. keyn Malkin.

00:03:16.183 --> 00:03:17.341
Malkin.

00:03:17.432 --> 00:03:18.168
yo.

00:03:18.090 --> 00:03:19.400
in Malkin

00:03:19.913 --> 00:03:22.253
iz geshtanen daytshn mit gruz

00:03:22.253 --> 00:03:25.480
un geshlogn di yidn in eyn zayt, di polyakn in andere zayt.

00:03:25.480 --> 00:03:27.130
⟨di⟩ polyakn ⟨hobn gevolt⟩ handlen.

00:03:27.912 --> 00:03:31.044
nakher fun Malkin zenen mir geganen in ZAREBY KOSCIELNE.

00:03:31.168 --> 00:03:32.861
hot ir a mol prubirt

00:03:32.861 --> 00:03:34.875
hobn yidn a mol prubirt

00:03:34.881 --> 00:03:38.891
tsu gebn tsurik, tsu shlogn tsurik di daytshn tsi di polyakn?

00:03:38.877 --> 00:03:42.941
s'iz geven a fal in Gritse, UNK bald dershosn.

00:03:42.964 --> 00:03:44.628
m'hot UNK dershosn.

00:03:45.057 --> 00:03:45.878
n-

00:03:48.465 --> 00:03:51.817
es iz geshtanen tsvey TRUCKn, groyse TRUCKn

00:03:52.060 --> 00:03:54.180
eyns far mener, eyns far froyen.

00:03:54.180 --> 00:03:57.690
UNK iz geshtanen a koleyke. hunderter mentshn zenen geganen.

00:03:57.690 --> 00:03:59.900
m'hot oysgetun gants naket.

00:04:00.312 --> 00:04:01.571
vu iz dos geven?

00:04:00.328 --> 00:04:03.882
m'hot alts, in ZAREBY KOSCIELNE.

00:04:02.623 --> 00:04:03.916
bay di grenets?

00:04:04.159 --> 00:04:06.737
alts tsugenumen, alts vos m'hot farmogt.

00:04:06.737 --> 00:04:07.949
alts.

00:04:08.007 --> 00:04:09.851
⟨geshtanen⟩ a groyser koysh

00:04:09.851 --> 00:04:11.881
an elterer daytsh iz gezitsn

00:04:12.310 --> 00:04:13.721
alts tsugenumen

00:04:14.706 --> 00:04:15.763
aroysgelozt

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:17.198
THAT'S ALL

00:04:18.402 --> 00:04:21.163
loz zhe zayn naket un borves UNK ikh gey

00:04:21.404 --> 00:04:23.002
un m'iz antlofn.

00:04:23.667 --> 00:04:24.845
m'iz gekumen keyn

00:04:24.845 --> 00:04:26.141
Byalistok.

00:04:27.042 --> 00:04:30.495
az i- dos iz geven in Malkin vos dos iz geshen?

00:04:29.539 --> 00:04:32.958
dos iz geven in Malkin, di TRUCKS. tsvey TRUCKS geshtanen.

00:04:32.847 --> 00:04:35.389
az yetst az ir zent arayn in Malkin?

00:04:35.293 --> 00:04:36.670
yo, UNK.

00:04:35.698 --> 00:04:37.902
un vi lang zent ir geblibn dortn?

00:04:37.673 --> 00:04:43.961
in Malkin hob ikh nisht gevoynt. m'iz geven bay a por shtundn. m'iz ⟨azoy⟩ vayter. m'iz geganen tsu fus durkh di grenets.

00:04:43.545 --> 00:04:44.922
biz vanet?

00:04:44.929 --> 00:04:46.374
biz Byalistok.

00:04:45.807 --> 00:04:48.838
biz Byalistok. vi vayt avek iz Byalistok?

00:04:52.725 --> 00:04:55.014
vi lang hot es genumen ahintsukumen?

00:04:55.678 --> 00:04:58.524
ver gedenkt? m'iz geganen, ikh un mayn shvester.

00:04:58.598 --> 00:04:59.857
di vos iz umgekumen.

00:04:59.577 --> 00:05:04.481
i- ay- aykh un a shvester in a- un ayer man, neyn?

00:05:03.306 --> 00:05:04.970
NO, ⟨undz⟩ aleyn.

00:05:05.719 --> 00:05:07.670
ikh un mayn shvester zenen geganen.

00:05:08.419 --> 00:05:10.117
az vu iz geven der man?

00:05:10.107 --> 00:05:12.986
mayn man, mayn man iz geven in Visoke Litovsk.

00:05:13.718 --> 00:05:15.419
hot dokh gearbet shoyn dort

00:05:15.419 --> 00:05:17.221
vi a beker, gevorn a beker.

00:05:17.211 --> 00:05:19.410
ober ir hot gezogt az ir zent

00:05:19.410 --> 00:05:21.356
a- antlofn mit im, yo?

00:05:20.907 --> 00:05:24.296
di ershte tsayt, di ershte tsayt. ikh bin tsurikgeganen fun dort

00:05:23.016 --> 00:05:24.259
in yanuar.

00:05:24.296 --> 00:05:31.768
yo, tsurikgeganen nokh ontuekhts nemen in di heym, a kleydl a vos UNK ontsutun, bin ikh geforn naket un borves, UNK avek antlofn.

00:05:31.504 --> 00:05:33.969
az ven ir ⟨ven⟩ tsurikgeforn

00:05:33.969 --> 00:05:35.939
vu iz der man geven? er iz shoyn geven

00:05:34.980 --> 00:05:40.019
er iz geblibn dort. er iz geblibn. ikh aleyn bin geganen, un er iz geblibn in Visoke Litevst.

00:05:36.246 --> 00:05:37.640
in Malkin?

00:05:37.647 --> 00:05:38.704
in Malk-

00:05:40.414 --> 00:05:42.956
un dan ven ir z- ir zent tsurikgekumen

00:05:43.013 --> 00:05:44.795
iz er geven in Visoke Litevsk.

00:05:44.717 --> 00:05:46.618
az ir zayt tsugegangen tsun im?

00:05:46.101 --> 00:05:47.478
yo, yo.

00:05:47.839 --> 00:05:50.533
m'hot gehat a voynung dort, ⟨gekrign a⟩ voynung.

00:05:50.202 --> 00:05:53.081
ober ir, ir zayt frier geven in Byalistok.

00:05:53.408 --> 00:05:59.899
Byalistok BEFORE. nakher zenen mir gan keyn BRZESZCZ. BRZESZCZ LITOWSK, un nokh BRZESZCZ LITOWSK iz z- iz Visoke Litovsk.

00:06:00.293 --> 00:06:01.420
iz vi lang

00:06:01.420 --> 00:06:03.392
hot es genumen biz ir hot UNK

00:06:02.689 --> 00:06:07.897
s'iz geven toyznter mentshn in di ban. m'iz oyf di dekher geshtanen, oyf di UNK

00:06:12.122 --> 00:06:15.676
az m'hot dos ibergelebt, az m'hot dos ibergehaltn

00:06:18.906 --> 00:06:21.181
az ir zayt fun Malkin

00:06:21.181 --> 00:06:23.929
keyn,

00:06:26.280 --> 00:06:29.036
zog mir nokh a mol, fun Malkin frier

00:06:29.036 --> 00:06:30.189
biz tsu

00:06:30.060 --> 00:06:31.691
ZAREBY KOSCIELNE.

00:06:31.782 --> 00:06:32.856
un dernokh

00:06:32.541 --> 00:06:36.095
fun ZAREBY KOSCIELNE keyn Byalistok. fun Byalistok keyn BRZESZCZ.

00:06:34.397 --> 00:06:35.184
u-

00:06:35.578 --> 00:06:38.626
un vi lang hot es genumen, di gantse tsayt?

00:06:37.873 --> 00:06:39.672
shoen, shoen.

00:06:39.595 --> 00:06:40.298
ah.

00:06:40.438 --> 00:06:42.038
biz ir zent gekumen

00:06:40.692 --> 00:06:42.086
shoen.

00:06:42.038 --> 00:06:43.233
tsu ayer man

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:43.841
yo, yo.

00:06:44.117 --> 00:06:46.358
un vi lang zent ir geblibn dortn?

00:06:46.358 --> 00:06:48.279
in Visoke Li- Litovsk?

00:06:48.100 --> 00:06:54.205
m'hot, m'hot undz arayngefirt tsu a poyer, tsu a krist, ⟨vayl⟩ me zol undz gebn oyf nakht shlofn

00:06:54.205 --> 00:06:58.708
m'hot geleygt shtroy oyf der erd. ikh bin gelign UNK vi se ⟨heybt⟩ on togn in di fri zenen mir aroys.

00:07:00.300 --> 00:07:01.306
nu

00:07:02.140 --> 00:07:05.441
un vi lang zent ir geven in, in, in Visoke Litovsk?

00:07:06.848 --> 00:07:10.824
vi lang ikh hob gevoynt dort? nisht lang. s'hot undz eyner gemasert.

00:07:11.050 --> 00:07:12.920
s'iz gekumen eyner tsu forn fun

00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:14.031
Gritse

00:07:14.138 --> 00:07:16.646
un hot gezogt az do voynen bundistn.

00:07:18.289 --> 00:07:21.742
un s'hot eyner ⟨undzer a⟩ bakonter iz dort geven a bukhhalter

00:07:22.238 --> 00:07:25.134
in di ⟨MOVIES⟩. s'iz geven komunistn demolt.

00:07:25.461 --> 00:07:31.867
un m'hot im gezogt UNK a RAJTER, do a Beker, der hot er gehert di nemen, iz er gekumen tsu morgns undz zogn

00:07:32.076 --> 00:07:34.224
"antloyfts, vayl s'iz zeyer

00:07:34.224 --> 00:07:35.529
m'vet enk shisn."

00:07:35.620 --> 00:07:36.457
yo.

00:07:36.649 --> 00:07:38.330
zenen mir antlofn

00:07:38.742 --> 00:07:39.546
UNK

00:07:40.075 --> 00:07:42.825
m'iz arayn in di velder arayn, hot er gehat a PRZEWODNIK.

00:07:42.825 --> 00:07:47.785
hot er undz tsugegebn a PLECAK mitn esn mitn ontuekhts, antlofn UNK nisht vu tsu geyn

00:07:47.785 --> 00:07:49.745
UNK

00:07:49.745 --> 00:07:51.341
m'hot nisht ⟨geven⟩ groyse velder

00:07:52.427 --> 00:07:56.353
un zenen gekumen, UNK der zelber polyak vos er hot undz tsugenumen

00:07:56.545 --> 00:07:58.851
polyak, ukrainer, ikh veys vos zenen geven

00:08:00.696 --> 00:08:05.038
un mayns a kuzin ⟨zogt⟩ er hot gezogt "du host dokh undz tsugenumen. du host undz gefirt. m-"

00:08:05.038 --> 00:08:06.595
zogt er "ikh?"

00:08:06.990 --> 00:08:09.667
un shoyn, m'hot undz avekgefirt in tfise keyn Br-

00:08:09.673 --> 00:08:11.236
keyn Brisk

00:08:11.715 --> 00:08:13.160
iz men gezitsn

00:08:12.508 --> 00:08:14.004
ale tsuzamen?

00:08:13.707 --> 00:08:14.581
ale.

00:08:14.128 --> 00:08:16.147
dos heyst ayer man

00:08:14.581 --> 00:08:18.257
bazunder mener, bazunder froyen. in gantsn bazunder

00:08:17.757 --> 00:08:21.176
ober ale zenen gegangen in gefengenish?

00:08:18.499 --> 00:08:20.163
ale tsunezamen.

00:08:20.727 --> 00:08:21.733
ye.

00:08:22.296 --> 00:08:27.504
m'hot undz arayngefirt in tfise, iz geven hunderter mentshn shoyn, hunderter mentshn.

00:08:27.544 --> 00:08:30.035
un vi lang zent ir geblibn in tfise?

00:08:30.683 --> 00:08:32.840
⟨efsher a⟩ knap yor

00:08:32.840 --> 00:08:34.575
ven der DEUTSCH iz ongefaln

00:08:35.053 --> 00:08:36.127
oyf

00:08:36.235 --> 00:08:37.649
oyf Rusland

00:08:37.649 --> 00:08:40.279
hot men undz aroysgenumen fun tfise, di rusn

00:08:40.279 --> 00:08:42.499
un zey hobn undz avekgefirt in a lager arayn.

00:08:43.457 --> 00:08:45.796
zey hobn undz gekhapt, gefirt azoy vi a

00:08:46.309 --> 00:08:50.437
m'hot undz gefirt zeks vokhn. mir zenen mir geforn mit KONSKI vagonen.

00:08:50.933 --> 00:08:51.922
biz

00:08:51.743 --> 00:08:54.099
biz in a lager, STANTSIYA YAYA.

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:56.546
vu, dos iz in Sibir?

00:08:56.029 --> 00:08:57.018
Sibir.

00:08:57.700 --> 00:09:02.134
un in di ts- in dem, durkh dem yor vos ir zent geven in tfise

00:09:02.134 --> 00:09:04.393
zent ir geven in farbindung mit ayer man?

00:09:05.344 --> 00:09:07.987
kh'hob finef yor nisht gevust in gantsn vu er iz.

00:09:07.757 --> 00:09:08.915
finef yor?

00:09:08.432 --> 00:09:09.438
finef yor.

00:09:09.327 --> 00:09:11.835
ir hot nit gevust tsi er lebt tsi nit?

00:09:12.668 --> 00:09:16.661
keyner vos hot aykh nisht gegebn keyn nayes? gornit.

00:09:16.296 --> 00:09:22.955
m'iz aheymgekumen keyn Poyln, hot er zikh gevust az ikh bin aheymgekumen a vokh frier tsi a vokh shpeter, ikh gedenk nisht, a vokh frier

00:09:22.118 --> 00:09:23.822
dos iz nokhn krig?

00:09:23.451 --> 00:09:24.417
nokhn krig.

00:09:23.822 --> 00:09:27.277
ober durkh di finef yor hot ir gornisht gevust.

00:09:24.670 --> 00:09:27.277
NO, finef yor nisht gevust gornisht.

00:09:27.450 --> 00:09:31.359
az mit vemen zent ir geven in S- in tfise? mit d- mit a shvester?

00:09:30.893 --> 00:09:33.452
NO, NO, mayne shvester ⟨zenen⟩ geven baym daytsh.

00:09:33.475 --> 00:09:35.176
al- ale zenen geven in

00:09:34.335 --> 00:09:35.881
ale geven ⟨baym daytsh⟩.

00:09:35.176 --> 00:09:38.126
az mit vemen zayt ir geven? mit fraynt? mit ku-

00:09:36.360 --> 00:09:39.898
kuzin, mit fraynt, mit kuzin, mayne tsvey kuzin.

00:09:38.622 --> 00:09:39.966
vi hobn geheysn

00:09:40.107 --> 00:09:42.075
eyne lebt. zi iz in NEW YORK.

00:09:41.760 --> 00:09:42.884
vi heyst zi?

00:09:42.958 --> 00:09:47.744
Khantshe. zi lebt. zi iz geven mit mir, un eyne iz in Yisroel.

00:09:48.223 --> 00:09:50.427
zi lebt. ir man lebt nisht. zi lebt.

00:09:50.485 --> 00:09:52.251
in eynem geven in tfise.

00:09:51.750 --> 00:09:54.663
un mit velekhe fraynt? vi hobn zey geheysn?

00:09:57.066 --> 00:10:01.245
ikh hob gehat a sakh fraynt, UNK ver gedenkt shoyn, Lodzher, Varshever

00:10:01.605 --> 00:10:06.661
geven hunderter mentshn, un yede por vokhn, UNK

00:10:06.898 --> 00:10:09.000
YOU KNOW vos dos iz?

00:10:09.160 --> 00:10:13.088
⟨fremde⟩ mit di shmates un gekumen an andere may- bafrayte

00:10:13.088 --> 00:10:14.543
an andere CELA

00:10:14.543 --> 00:10:19.099
un a por tog UNK, an andere CELA, azoy az

00:10:20.843 --> 00:10:25.393
un m'hot ibergelbt UNK azoy fil yorn aleyn, finef yor UNK.

00:10:25.922 --> 00:10:30.067
az ir zent geven dos, di gantse tsayt in, in, in zelbn ort?

00:10:30.411 --> 00:10:31.569
in Sibir?

00:10:30.850 --> 00:10:34.998
ye, yor. in tfise bin ikh gezitsn a knap yor

00:10:34.998 --> 00:10:38.049
⟨NACH⟩ dem hot men undz avekgefirt in lager oykhet a knap yor.

00:10:38.393 --> 00:10:41.519
in lager hot gearbet in a

00:10:38.460 --> 00:10:39.854
vi hot es e-

00:10:41.519 --> 00:10:46.000
der fabrik fun VOENNE ontuekhtsn far, far SOLDIERS

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:48.241
hoyzn un GYMNASTYORKAS

00:10:47.860 --> 00:10:50.199
vos hor ir geton? ir hot zey geneyt?

00:10:49.699 --> 00:10:54.907
ikh hob geneyt, ⟨iz⟩ vos den? ikh hob gearbet. ikh hob nisht gearbet, volt ikh nisht gehat keyn shtikl broyt tsu esn.

00:10:56.213 --> 00:10:58.266
az dos iz geven in velkhn lager?

00:10:58.288 --> 00:11:00.239
YAYA. STANTSIYA YAYA.

00:10:59.875 --> 00:11:01.168
STANTSIYA YAYA.

00:11:01.562 --> 00:11:04.171
un ir UNK dortn geven a yortsayt?

00:11:04.144 --> 00:11:06.821
yo, s'iz geven dort a sakh ge-

00:11:06.945 --> 00:11:07.681
mh

00:11:07.873 --> 00:11:09.014
barakn

00:11:09.088 --> 00:11:12.271
zeyer a sakh bar- UNK a groyse UNK

00:11:13.442 --> 00:11:16.845
s'iz geven politishe arestirte iz geven bazunder opgeteylt

00:11:16.952 --> 00:11:19.489
un mir ⟨polyakn⟩, polyakn un yidn

00:11:19.489 --> 00:11:20.603
oykh bazunder.

00:11:20.603 --> 00:11:25.711
s'iz geven polyakn oykhet, ober polyakn ⟨hot men⟩ arestirt far handl, far shmuglen, far andere za-

00:11:25.711 --> 00:11:27.876
m'hot nisht arestirt keyn polyak vayl er iz a polyak.

00:11:28.680 --> 00:11:30.530
a yid hot men fa- iz geven

00:11:30.621 --> 00:11:32.977
⟨PRZEZACet⟩ tsu shisn, THAT'S ALL.

00:11:34.198 --> 00:11:35.930
 s'iz gut geven.

00:11:36.865 --> 00:11:38.783
m'hot ibergelebt finef yor,

00:11:41.843 --> 00:11:42.849
⟨vest⟩

00:11:43.007 --> 00:11:44.384
kent zikh forshteln.

00:11:46.686 --> 00:11:47.945
vos ken men tun?

00:11:48.373 --> 00:11:50.274
ir zet az ikh bin geblibn lebn

00:11:50.398 --> 00:11:51.759
me vil lebn.

00:11:54.432 --> 00:11:58.189
az in STANTSIYA YAYA UNK zaynen geven eyn yor.

00:11:58.347 --> 00:11:59.050
ye.

00:11:58.853 --> 00:12:00.112
un nokh dem?

00:12:00.507 --> 00:12:03.758
nokh dem iz geven SHIKORSKI's bafrayung.

00:12:03.780 --> 00:12:05.006
di amnestye.

00:12:05.822 --> 00:12:07.267
in velkhn, dos iz geven

00:12:05.839 --> 00:12:08.687
hobn zey UNK ⟨hot men undz⟩ nokh nisht gevolt aroyslozn.

00:12:08.687 --> 00:12:10.912
ikh hob gemakht fir normes.

00:12:11.509 --> 00:12:12.600
fir vos?

00:12:11.610 --> 00:12:15.164
fir normes. ir veyst ⟨vos⟩ a norme iz?

00:12:15.255 --> 00:12:19.316
UNK a norme iz zeyer a sakh

00:12:20.065 --> 00:12:22.748
hobn zey geflegt tsu zogn UNK

00:12:22.748 --> 00:12:24.153
CHERT V RUKACH

00:12:24.153 --> 00:12:27.546
vos m'hot mir gegebn hob ikh gemakht. vos m'hot mir gegebn hob ikh gemakht.

00:12:27.945 --> 00:12:30.723
dort UNK oyfhengen?

00:12:29.970 --> 00:12:30.841
vos meynt dos?

00:12:32.299 --> 00:12:33.423
vos meynt dos?

00:12:33.396 --> 00:12:36.782
m- m'hot ⟨mir⟩ gegebn a shtikl broyt tsu esn, iz geven UNK leym.

00:12:36.788 --> 00:12:40.596
teyl mol hot men tsvey vokhn nisht gegebn keyn broyt. s'iz nisht geven. zey hobn oykh nisht gehat.

00:12:44.466 --> 00:12:47.582
az dos iz, di amnestye iz geven in eyn in fertsik?

00:12:46.187 --> 00:12:47.581
di amnestye.

00:12:47.723 --> 00:12:49.067
di amnestye iz ge-

00:12:47.790 --> 00:12:50.622
far ale pol- poylishe birger. far poylishe birger.

00:12:50.558 --> 00:12:51.446
az

00:12:50.622 --> 00:12:54.838
hobn zey undz nokh nisht gevolt aroyslozn fun lager. s'iz a shod geven. ⟨host⟩ gearbet bekhinem

00:12:56.127 --> 00:13:01.421
iz a mol gekumen VOE- VOENNE mentshn tsvey mit tsvey rusishe.

00:13:01.421 --> 00:13:02.991
m'hot ⟨tsugegebn⟩. m'hot ongeshtelt

00:13:02.991 --> 00:13:04.069
di fabrik

00:13:04.193 --> 00:13:05.472
ongeshtelt di fabrik

00:13:05.472 --> 00:13:08.861
m'hot oysge⟨UNK⟩ oyf a tsetl di ale poylishe birger, di nemen

00:13:08.985 --> 00:13:10.784
oys⟨UNK⟩ UNK aroysgelozt.

00:13:11.466 --> 00:13:13.333
un vu zayt ir demolst gegangen?

00:13:13.558 --> 00:13:18.631
demolst hobn zey undz gegebn a por shikh ontsutun, epes a shmate yake ontsutun

00:13:18.908 --> 00:13:21.855
un zey hobn undz gegebn a por z- a por, a por rubl

00:13:22.148 --> 00:13:23.745
far TICKETS

00:13:23.818 --> 00:13:25.331
vu me vil forn.

00:13:25.422 --> 00:13:28.082
⟨bay undz hot er⟩ gehat a bakontn a rusishn, zogt er

00:13:28.408 --> 00:13:35.236
"kinder, forts nisht in ⟨di heym⟩. UNK shtarbn oys di ale BEZHNETSES. zey shtarbn oys UNK epidemye iz a groyse

00:13:35.293 --> 00:13:36.721
forts keyn Sibir."

00:13:36.947 --> 00:13:38.696
zenen mir geforn keyn Sibir.

00:13:38.500 --> 00:13:40.519
⟨az⟩ ir zent shoyn geven in Sibir, neyn?

00:13:40.187 --> 00:13:42.428
nu, yo, ober nokh a mol ⟨forn in⟩ Sibir.

00:13:42.428 --> 00:13:44.301
iz dos zeyer groys, Sibir.

00:13:44.301 --> 00:13:47.538
m'iz geforn ⟨durkh⟩ a shtetl b- nisht vayt fun UNK TURA

00:13:45.722 --> 00:13:47.032
vu zayt i-

00:13:47.680 --> 00:13:48.605
nisht vayt

00:13:48.605 --> 00:13:50.559
m'hot gedungen zikh a shtibele

00:13:50.616 --> 00:13:52.837
bay a ⟨CHAZIAJKA⟩, bar a

00:13:53.518 --> 00:13:54.440
un m'hot

00:13:54.835 --> 00:13:58.356
m'hot undz UNK gegebn, demolts iz geven di ergste tsayt.

00:13:58.767 --> 00:14:00.836
m'hot geshtorbn far hunger.

00:14:01.737 --> 00:14:06.675
m'hot nisht gekrign keyn shtikl broyt. m'hot nisht gornisht gegat. bin naket un borves.

00:14:08.301 --> 00:14:13.748
nakher, m'hot shoyn gekrign arbet. m'iz geganen tsu UNK SOVYET, hobn zey undz gegebn arbet

00:14:13.748 --> 00:14:17.171
in a, a hotel fun invalidn

00:14:18.038 --> 00:14:21.424
bar a mashinl. gedreyt mit a korbe.

00:14:21.143 --> 00:14:22.706
vos iz, vos

00:14:21.801 --> 00:14:26.216
mit di hant. mit di hant hot men gedreyt di mashinl. a ney mashin.

00:14:23.640 --> 00:14:25.642
vos far a mashin iz dos geven?

00:14:25.716 --> 00:14:26.486
ah.

00:14:27.387 --> 00:14:29.153
oykhet VOENNE UNK.

00:14:30.559 --> 00:14:33.573
m'hot dort gearbet epes a tsayt

00:14:35.065 --> 00:14:37.185
un shoyn. nakher mir ze'mir avekgeforn.

00:14:37.326 --> 00:14:40.897
vi lang zaynt ir ge- ge- ha- hot ir gearbet dortn?

00:14:40.768 --> 00:14:43.630
kh'hob nisht keyn anung. UNK vi lang m'iz dort geven.

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:48.122
m'hot dort nisht gekrign batsolt.

00:14:48.122 --> 00:14:49.300
alts bekhinem.

00:14:49.476 --> 00:14:52.594
UNK

00:14:52.594 --> 00:14:56.999
ir veyst vos dos iz? az m'vet aheymforn, ⟨veln⟩ zey undz gebn dos gelt vos m'hot opgearbet.

00:14:56.999 --> 00:14:59.224
UNK.

00:14:59.955 --> 00:15:01.501
hot ir gehat vos tsu esn?

00:15:02.419 --> 00:15:04.507
yede tsvey vokhn a shtikele broyt.

00:15:04.507 --> 00:15:08.520
bin eyn mol aroysgeganen oyfn gortn, hob ikh nisht gekent. ikh bin gezitsn UNK ⟨bar a mashin⟩

00:15:08.882 --> 00:15:11.373
hob ikh aroysgerisn a mer, a merl.

00:15:11.582 --> 00:15:14.225
nu, hot mikh gekhapt. m'hot mikh gekhapt.

00:15:14.991 --> 00:15:17.519
mikh bald gegan aroysshikn in tfise arayn.

00:15:17.519 --> 00:15:18.477
yo.

00:15:18.754 --> 00:15:22.916
hobn zey di ale arbeter ongehoybn veynen, vayl ikh bin geven a guter arbeter

00:15:23.108 --> 00:15:26.578
⟨me zol⟩ bay di UNK ⟨mir⟩ geshenkt dos ershte mol.

00:15:26.753 --> 00:15:28.519
nisht oyfhengen.

00:15:30.145 --> 00:15:33.328
s'iz geven ZAKRITI STOLOVIYES, farmakhte STOLOVIYES

00:15:33.638 --> 00:15:38.171
vos di N.K.V.D. ⟨un nokh azoy vayter⟩ UNK gegesn getrunken fun bestn

00:15:38.312 --> 00:15:40.367
un di arbeter geshtorbn far hunger.

00:15:40.367 --> 00:15:42.997
keyn mener hot men nisht gezen. ⟨zenen zey⟩ alts geven oyf di milkhome.

00:15:43.982 --> 00:15:45.767
gornisht, UNK aleyn oykh gehungert.

00:15:45.767 --> 00:15:47.114
⟨hot men undz⟩ oykh gehungert.

00:15:49.703 --> 00:15:55.125
in dray un fertsikstn yor iz shoyn a bisl laykhter gevorn. m'hot gekrign a shtikl erd.

00:15:55.125 --> 00:15:56.903
bloyz berg iz geven.

00:15:57.482 --> 00:16:02.887
m'hot gezetst kartoflyes. az m'hot nisht gehat vos tsu zetsn, hot men geganvet sholn fun kartoflyes

00:16:02.887 --> 00:16:05.357
hot men gezetst di sholekhts, zeyer a gute ⟨erd⟩ geven dortn.

00:16:06.021 --> 00:16:09.947
m'hot aropgenumen dray hundert un zekhtsik WIADRAS kartoflyes.

00:16:10.020 --> 00:16:11.533
hot men gehat tsu esn

00:16:11.657 --> 00:16:15.701
kartoflyes, trinken kartoflyes, azoy kartoflyes, azoy ⟨m'hot gegesn⟩.

00:16:18.205 --> 00:16:20.561
shoyn nakher gekumen di tsayt. m'iz avekgeforn

00:16:21.580 --> 00:16:27.514
m'iz gezitsn in tfise oykhet a bisl. m'hot undz gevolt gebn pasport, az nisht hot men nisht gevolt nemen

00:16:27.807 --> 00:16:30.788
s'iz geven a poylishe PLACOWKA, UNK me zol nisht nemen.

00:16:30.625 --> 00:16:31.817
⟨ver⟩ iz dos geven?

00:16:32.042 --> 00:16:34.145
poylishe PLACOWKA iz geven

00:16:34.962 --> 00:16:36.879
ikh gedenk nisht vi di shtot heyst.

00:16:38.573 --> 00:16:40.997
az ir hot nisht gevolt nemen keyn pasport.

00:16:39.923 --> 00:16:43.151
NO, m'hot nisht genumen keyn pasport. UNK dos

00:16:42.066 --> 00:16:43.325
far vos nit?

00:16:43.151 --> 00:16:46.583
vayl UNK hot moyre gehat, vet men nisht kenen aroysforn keyn mol.

00:16:46.842 --> 00:16:48.439
m'hot gevolt aheymforn.

00:16:49.069 --> 00:16:51.155
UNK zen di mame mitn tatn.

00:16:52.512 --> 00:16:53.923
iz

00:16:56.258 --> 00:16:58.496
hot men gebidevet, THAT'S ALL.

00:16:59.802 --> 00:17:03.441
shoyn zeks un fertsikstn yor zenen mir aheymgeforn.

00:17:07.075 --> 00:17:11.136
aheymgekumen, keynem nisht getrofn. bloyz tsvey shvester zenen geblibn.

00:17:10.787 --> 00:17:13.222
ir zent geven in, in, in, in Gritse?

00:17:13.116 --> 00:17:15.877
yo. vos far a frage?

00:17:13.222 --> 00:17:14.224
dos heyst?

00:17:16.221 --> 00:17:20.284
bin geganen oyfn besoylem ⟨aroys⟩zen vu iz efsher a keyver, efsher vos

00:17:20.284 --> 00:17:25.293
hobn zey aroysge⟨numen⟩ ale matseyves, tsehakt alding, ⟨ZGLADZet⟩ di gantse erd.

00:17:25.671 --> 00:17:26.846
gornisht geven.

00:17:28.084 --> 00:17:30.063
UNK vos far a frage UNK

00:17:30.063 --> 00:17:32.887
bay UNK iz geven UNK dos gevelb

00:17:33.012 --> 00:17:35.925
iz geshtanen di struzhke geshtanen dort

00:17:36.741 --> 00:17:38.929
⟨iz ir⟩ gevelb yetst geven

00:17:43.120 --> 00:17:44.042
az

00:17:44.301 --> 00:17:46.455
ven ir zent aroys fun Sibir

00:17:47.710 --> 00:17:53.188
ir ho- ir hot dortn in, in Sibir no- nokh STANTSIYA YAYA hot ir gearbet nokhet a yor in Sibir.

00:17:52.435 --> 00:17:53.798
yo, avade.

00:17:53.798 --> 00:17:56.310
UNK droysn, nor vu ⟨volt⟩ ikh gehat tsu esn.

00:17:56.923 --> 00:17:59.650
s'iz geven in zelbn ort di gantse tsayt?

00:17:59.218 --> 00:18:01.844
NO, nisht STANTSIYA YAYA, UNK

00:18:00.012 --> 00:18:01.862
ikh hob nisht UNK farshtanen.

00:18:01.902 --> 00:18:04.731
m'iz fun STANTSIYA YAYA geforn keyn tif Sibir.

00:18:04.585 --> 00:18:07.819
yo, un vi lang zent ir geven in tif Sibir?

00:18:05.243 --> 00:18:06.621
iz dort hob i-

00:18:07.150 --> 00:18:08.285
 a knap yor

00:18:08.285 --> 00:18:15.381
dort hob ikh gebetn arbet. bin gelofn in UNK SOVYETSK, UNK vi hot dos geheysn UNK gedenk zey. hot men undz gegebn. s'iz geven an artel

00:18:15.381 --> 00:18:17.961
fun bloyz invalidn.

00:18:18.557 --> 00:18:20.525
un vi lang zaynt ir geven dortn?

00:18:22.641 --> 00:18:24.710
ikh gedenk nisht vi lang.

00:18:26.505 --> 00:18:27.326
ikh gedenk nisht.

00:18:27.180 --> 00:18:29.182
un fun dortn, vu zayt ir gegangen?

00:18:28.615 --> 00:18:29.790
aheymgeforn.

00:18:29.560 --> 00:18:32.490
ah, dos iz shoyn geven in zeks un fertsik, ah.

00:18:29.813 --> 00:18:30.853
aheym.

00:18:31.045 --> 00:18:33.233
yo, di amnestye.

00:18:33.593 --> 00:18:36.118
az ir zayt geforn keyn, keyn Gritse

00:18:36.343 --> 00:18:39.948
bin geforn keyn Lodzh dos ershte. ikh hob derhaltn a briv fun mayn shvester.

00:18:37.761 --> 00:18:38.750
Lodzh

00:18:40.545 --> 00:18:44.066
kh'hob dokh keseyder geshribn magistrat, magistrat, magistrat.

00:18:44.157 --> 00:18:47.055
⟨iz zey hobn⟩ ongekumen a briv fun mayn shvester. zi voynt in Lodzh.

00:18:47.055 --> 00:18:49.726
bin ikh glaykh geforn keyn Lodzh, UNK

00:18:48.139 --> 00:18:51.322
vu zayt ir geven ven ir hot bakumen, dem briv?

00:18:50.873 --> 00:18:54.157
ikh hob geneyt dort in artel ⟨ale⟩ fun di invalidn.

00:18:54.130 --> 00:18:56.351
az in Sibir hot ir bakumen a briv?

00:18:56.172 --> 00:18:57.212
yo.

00:18:57.100 --> 00:18:58.899
in Sibir fun Lodzh?

00:18:58.483 --> 00:18:59.321
ye.

00:18:59.445 --> 00:19:04.079
az zi iz geblibn lebn mit di yingste shvester geblibn lebn, in lager baym daytsh.

00:19:04.373 --> 00:19:06.259
hot zi aykh dertseylt

00:19:06.010 --> 00:19:08.198
farshtendlekh hot zi mir alts dertseylt.

00:19:06.259 --> 00:19:09.581
vos iz ge- geshen i- in dem briv?

00:19:09.064 --> 00:19:11.066
NO, NO, nisht in briv, NO.

00:19:11.815 --> 00:19:15.032
az ir zent aheym keyn, ir zent keyn Lodzh gegangen, un zi hot

00:19:16.320 --> 00:19:18.477
ir zayt geven mitn, mit der shvester

00:19:18.477 --> 00:19:22.980
un zi hot ⟨dir⟩ demolst dertseylt vegn di eltern un vegn di andere shve-

00:19:21.282 --> 00:19:23.318
ye, ye, ye, ye.

00:19:25.635 --> 00:19:29.392
iz zayt ir tsuzamen geforn ah keyn Gritse?

00:19:27.660 --> 00:19:29.459
NO, mir ze'mir ⟨aley-⟩

00:19:29.483 --> 00:19:34.691
ikh bin aleyn geforn keyn Gritse mit di kuzinke vos m'iz aheymgeforn fun lager.

00:19:34.090 --> 00:19:37.509
un ir hot gefunen dos hoyz vu ir flegt voynen?

00:19:38.005 --> 00:19:41.053
adurkhgegan, nokhn hoyz bin antlofn, UNK, nisht keyn

00:19:42.274 --> 00:19:43.837
emetser iz dortn geven?

00:19:43.641 --> 00:19:46.065
di struzhke's hot a tokhter geshtanen.

00:19:46.543 --> 00:19:48.174
⟨vos⟩ zey hobn dos ibergenumen?

00:19:48.417 --> 00:19:50.841
UNK nu, vos den? UNK genumen.

00:19:50.627 --> 00:19:53.338
iz vi lang zent ir geblibn in K- in ah Gritse?

00:19:53.125 --> 00:19:56.814
in Gritse bin ikh ⟨geven⟩ epes tsvey tog. geshlofn oyf a boydem UNK.

00:19:57.225 --> 00:19:59.446
un dernokh tsurik in Lodzh?

00:19:59.132 --> 00:20:02.804
tsurik keyn Lodzh. ⟨nakher⟩ geforn tsu di yingere shvester keyn DANZIG

00:20:03.148 --> 00:20:05.319
UNK in DANZIG.

00:20:05.443 --> 00:20:12.457
m'iz geforn tsu di shvester. geven do a bisl, do a bisl. keyn voynung hot men nisht gegat. ⟨m'iz shoyn⟩ bazetst in Poyln. m'hot gezen vos dervart undz in Poyln.

00:20:12.565 --> 00:20:14.502
bin geven biz tsu dem

00:20:14.502 --> 00:20:16.569
oysbrukh in Kelts.

00:20:16.569 --> 00:20:19.257
az m'hot gezen Kelts, zogt men me muz avek fun Poyln.

00:20:19.821 --> 00:20:22.498
m'hot zikh nisht bazetst in Poyln, un THAT'S ALL.

00:20:22.352 --> 00:20:26.548
ven zent ir v- gevorn fareynikt mitn man?

00:20:27.128 --> 00:20:28.539
in Gritse.

00:20:28.630 --> 00:20:30.058
in, ven?

00:20:29.170 --> 00:20:32.488
in zeks un fertsikstn yor. er iz gekumen zeks vokhn shpeter vi ikh.

00:20:32.697 --> 00:20:33.906
finef vo-

00:20:32.781 --> 00:20:35.087
az dortn ven ir zent geven

